00:01:11.439 --> 00:01:12.439
I heard

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:13.840
following today's court,

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:16.079
Duke Ying and Grand Tutor Liu

00:01:16.239 --> 00:01:17.200
were both assassinated.

00:01:19.640 --> 00:01:20.599
The Empress did it.

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:22.239
Yes.

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.040
Now, the palace

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:25.319
is heavily guarded.

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:28.439
Even a master thief like me
couldn't sneak in.

00:01:28.439 --> 00:01:30.280
She had co-opted
the Imperial Guard commander.

00:01:31.239 --> 00:01:32.719
With His Majesty's illness,

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:34.840
she tightened palace security,

00:01:35.719 --> 00:01:37.159
and controlled the Imperial Guard.

00:01:38.159 --> 00:01:39.200
And you're playing chess?

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.560
If we don't stay calm now,

00:01:44.359 --> 00:01:45.599
we'll never find a solution.

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:48.920
This Empress's ruthlessness is no less

00:01:48.959 --> 00:01:50.040
than Chancellor Huo's.

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:52.359
News came from Qi State.

00:01:53.319 --> 00:01:55.319
It says she has long colluded
with King Liang.

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.840
The Qi envoy will arrive
in the capital soon.

00:01:58.799 --> 00:01:59.760
It seems King Liang

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:02.519
has deep ties with the Empress.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:06.319
Now the Sheng army's name is cleared.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.919
The pieces we planted

00:02:10.039 --> 00:02:11.400
can finally be put to use.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:18.879
When the Qi envoy enters Chen,

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:20.639
I need you

00:02:21.439 --> 00:02:22.759
to use every means possible

00:02:23.159 --> 00:02:25.479
to delay the envoy
King Liang sends to the city.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:27.280
Seventeenth Prince,

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:29.479
the envoy entering Chen from Qi State

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:32.080
must be you.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:33.759
I will not fail.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:37.199
If I guess it right,

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:39.360
the palace will soon issue
a lockdown order.

00:02:40.639 --> 00:02:41.439
A lockdown order?

00:02:42.020 --> 00:02:44.280
The Empress took
all officials' families into the palace.

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:48.680
Her wolfish ambition
is now plain to see.

00:02:51.319 --> 00:02:53.960
Get into the palace
before the lockdown order is issued.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:56.319
Don't worry.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.000
Return to me alive.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:07.840
(Your Highness,)

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:10.120
(take care of yourself.)

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:11.800
(Once this is over,)

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:13.639
(we'll never be apart again.)

00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:19.960
Where are you?

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:22.599
Lady Yunfei.

00:03:23.560 --> 00:03:24.879
With heavy guard everywhere now,

00:03:24.919 --> 00:03:26.319
how do we escape this tightly

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:27.439
surrounded place?

00:03:27.439 --> 00:03:27.840
Yes.

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:29.400
Yeyou Court is where servants live.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:30.319
No one guards it.

00:03:30.479 --> 00:03:32.520
I must ask you all to bear
with this for now.

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:33.080
Follow me!

00:03:33.759 --> 00:03:34.280
Go!

00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:37.080
I deserve death.

00:03:37.400 --> 00:03:39.599
The Empress threatened
His Majesty's life,

00:03:39.879 --> 00:03:42.120
forcing me to surrender
the Imperial Guard token.

00:03:44.240 --> 00:03:45.319
Huo Wan burned her bridges.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:48.120
Such a brazen move
was beyond expectation.

00:03:50.112 --> 00:03:50.944
Not your fault.

00:03:51.319 --> 00:03:52.240
Take me to see Yu now.

00:03:52.479 --> 00:03:52.960
Yes.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.439
Your Majesty, I advise you

00:04:02.759 --> 00:04:04.759
to obediently draft the edict,

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:06.960
appointing me as regent.

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:09.879
We are husband and wife.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.479
Moreover, within my womb

00:04:14.360 --> 00:04:15.840
already lies your flesh and blood.

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:18.879
What is there to worry about?

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:37.680
Whether you draft this edict or not,

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:40.240
the throne will belong
to the child in my womb.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:44.519
Oh, right.

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:48.800
The imperial physician has checked it.

00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:52.279
It's a boy!

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:03.480
Yu.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:05.199
Get up.

00:05:07.519 --> 00:05:08.839
What did she make you drink?

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.040
Spit it out!

00:05:18.879 --> 00:05:19.600
Sister,

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:21.920
you are here.

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.040
In the end, you still

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.480
couldn't let go of me.

00:05:29.759 --> 00:05:30.519
Isn't that right?

00:05:31.319 --> 00:05:32.040
Don't worry.

00:05:32.639 --> 00:05:34.040
I've made all the arrangements.

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:40.360
I once served in the Sheng army.

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:42.959
I entered the Imperial Guard
by the Grand Princess's grace.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:45.439
For years, I've enjoyed
the imperial favor.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:49.920
I am willing
to sacrifice everything for you.

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:52.199
Sister,

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:54.600
I have long prepared an edict,

00:05:55.879 --> 00:05:56.680
appointing you

00:05:58.560 --> 00:05:59.600
to act as regent.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:01.680
Even if...

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:07.040
Even if I die one day,

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:08.839
in my heart...

00:06:11.279 --> 00:06:12.360
In my heart,

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:15.639
I have no regrets.

00:06:16.879 --> 00:06:17.839
You won't die.

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:20.199
You won't die.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:24.680
I will protect the Chen State

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:29.279
and you,

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:32.800
just like in the past.

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:42.920
Yu, lie down.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:06:59.519
Commander Wei.

00:06:59.879 --> 00:07:00.439
Here.

00:07:00.839 --> 00:07:01.680
Go spread the word.

00:07:03.839 --> 00:07:04.600
Say that

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:09.600
the Grand Princess did not die,

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:12.000
but the injuries stole her past.

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:16.120
The Lady Yunfei today

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:20.000
is the Grand Princess.

00:07:20.759 --> 00:07:21.360
This is

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.560
far too risky, isn't it?

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.399
The Empress...

00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:26.560
Just go spread the word.

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:28.639
The faster, the better.

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:30.199
Yes.

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:34.360
(Only by drawing
Huo Wan's attention to me)

00:07:34.959 --> 00:07:36.079
(will the ministers' family)

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:38.040
(stand a sliver of a chance.)

00:07:53.408 --> 00:07:55.519
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

00:07:55.519 --> 00:07:58.720
- Long live the Grand Princess.
- Long live the Grand Princess.

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:01.199
I got hurt and lost my memory for years.

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:03.240
I appreciate you remembering me.

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:05.560
From today onward,

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:09.199
you will remain by my side.

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:20.279
The Grand Princess perished

00:08:20.279 --> 00:08:22.079
in the fire of Weiyang Palace years ago.

00:08:22.759 --> 00:08:23.720
Lady Yunfei,

00:08:24.279 --> 00:08:25.920
how dare you impersonate her?

00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:27.600
Someone.

00:08:27.959 --> 00:08:29.040
Seize her!

00:08:29.519 --> 00:08:30.160
What?

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:34.000
That fire back then
didn't burn me to death.

00:08:34.960 --> 00:08:36.399
I crawled back from the abyss.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.159
You're scared now?

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:40.919
Nonsense!

00:08:41.279 --> 00:08:42.559
I saw you with her own eyes...

00:08:42.559 --> 00:08:44.039
Saw with your own eyes?

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:47.679
Then you must surely remember

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:52.000
how that fire started.

00:08:53.799 --> 00:08:56.200
Now, it's time for you
to taste that same bitterness.

00:08:57.559 --> 00:08:58.480
Why are you waiting?

00:08:59.039 --> 00:08:59.879
Kill this impostor

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.399
for me.

00:09:10.799 --> 00:09:11.720
His Majesty is weak,

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:13.600
granting me the authority of regent.

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:15.240
The Imperial Seal

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.399
carries His Majesty's authority.

00:09:19.559 --> 00:09:23.200
- Long live the Emperor!
- Long live the Emperor!

00:09:26.639 --> 00:09:29.000
I don't care if you're Lady Yunfei
or the Grand Princess.

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:31.440
This realm is already mine.

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:34.639
What use are your
most devoted subjects now?

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:37.519
Aren't you all kneeling
at my feet this very moment?

00:09:38.399 --> 00:09:39.240
Your life

00:09:39.919 --> 00:09:41.559
is also in my hands right now.

00:09:42.279 --> 00:09:43.279
Sheng Yunlin,

00:09:44.279 --> 00:09:46.960
did you think living a second life
would let you turn the tables?

00:09:50.039 --> 00:09:51.799
She defiled the dead
and offended the regent.

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:52.879
She merits death.

00:09:54.159 --> 00:09:55.279
Imperial Guards!

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:57.159
- Here!
- Here!

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:59.559
Execute this sorceress
by a thousand cuts!

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:05.879
Report!

00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:08.039
Qi envoy wants
to see the Grand Princess.

00:10:16.919 --> 00:10:18.039
I was unaware

00:10:20.279 --> 00:10:22.399
that the Qi envoy
was the Seventeenth Prince.

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:24.639
Pardon the delay.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.279
Grand Tutor Xie.

00:10:39.759 --> 00:10:40.879
It has been many days.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.440
I hadn't expected you

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:46.840
to have gone to welcome
the delegation on my behalf.

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:48.519
It was my duty.

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:50.720
I only did my utmost.

00:10:52.559 --> 00:10:54.240
Years ago, I heard

00:10:55.039 --> 00:10:56.240
that the Grand Princess died.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.480
My heart was deeply grieved.

00:10:59.840 --> 00:11:01.399
Now, seeing the Grand Princess safe,

00:11:01.840 --> 00:11:02.799
I am overjoyed.

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:08.039
The Grand Princess's grace today
surpasses even before,

00:11:08.519 --> 00:11:11.000
like a celestial maiden
descending to the mortal realm.

00:11:14.279 --> 00:11:15.759
You flatter me, Your Highness.

00:11:16.639 --> 00:11:19.240
You yourself are a young hero,

00:11:19.679 --> 00:11:20.639
remarkable in bearing.

00:11:23.759 --> 00:11:26.159
News travels remarkably fast
in your Qi State.

00:11:26.639 --> 00:11:28.159
The Grand Princess had barely returned

00:11:28.759 --> 00:11:30.159
and you rushed to seek an audience.

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:33.200
Back then,

00:11:34.159 --> 00:11:36.639
when the Seventeenth Prince
came from Qi to Chen,

00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:38.960
I vaguely recall it was to seek the hand

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:41.720
of the Grand Princess in marriage.

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:45.600
Who could have imagined

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:47.639
that a fire in Weiyang Palace

00:11:47.799 --> 00:11:49.840
would ruin that splendid match?

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:52.639
How about this?

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:54.360
Why not today?

00:11:54.759 --> 00:11:55.919
I'll play matchmaker

00:11:56.279 --> 00:11:59.120
and let you rekindle
your past romance, okay?

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:01.080
Since when did my marriage

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:05.320
become the Empress's place to decide?

00:12:16.279 --> 00:12:17.679
You couldn't possibly think

00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:20.720
that you're still ruling
behind the screen, do you?

00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:22.679
Open your eyes and see.

00:12:23.320 --> 00:12:24.519
In today's Chen State,

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:27.200
who's really holding the reins of power?

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:32.320
The Empress

00:12:32.759 --> 00:12:34.480
governs the Chen State now.

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:36.200
Your word is sacred.

00:12:36.759 --> 00:12:38.240
You can't jest with me.

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.840
My visit this time

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:41.159
brings only gifts.

00:12:41.519 --> 00:12:42.559
But if someday

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:44.240
I engage to the Grand Princess,

00:12:45.039 --> 00:12:45.879
within ten days

00:12:46.360 --> 00:12:48.159
I'll return
with a grand dowry procession

00:12:49.679 --> 00:12:51.600
delivered straight
to the Chen royal family.

00:12:52.799 --> 00:12:54.080
Since the Seventeenth Prince

00:12:54.639 --> 00:12:55.799
wishes to show sincerity,

00:12:57.639 --> 00:12:58.399
how about

00:12:59.039 --> 00:13:02.600
returning the lands
Chen State ceded three years ago

00:13:02.759 --> 00:13:03.759
as betrothal gifts?

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:05.440
One matter at a time.

00:13:06.879 --> 00:13:08.639
Her Highness has now agreed

00:13:09.720 --> 00:13:11.279
that if war resumes this year,

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:13.480
you must cede territory

00:13:15.159 --> 00:13:16.080
before ceasing fire.

00:13:20.919 --> 00:13:21.679
I

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:24.759
intend to reconcile with Qi State

00:13:26.759 --> 00:13:28.039
and restore friendly relations.

00:13:29.559 --> 00:13:30.519
Specific terms

00:13:31.159 --> 00:13:33.039
will be discussed another day
at Qinian Hall.

00:13:33.399 --> 00:13:35.320
Today, let's first welcome
the Seventeenth Prince

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:36.279
and his delegation.

00:13:38.679 --> 00:13:42.080
May Chen and Qi States
foster amicable relations,

00:13:42.279 --> 00:13:44.679
and may their people
live in peace and prosperity.

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:52.960
Lord Xie has instructed

00:13:53.159 --> 00:13:54.399
time is limited. Act swiftly.

00:13:54.519 --> 00:13:55.000
Yes.

00:13:59.399 --> 00:14:01.559
I know some antidote techniques.

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:03.159
For Your Majesty...

00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:23.120
Well...

00:14:25.039 --> 00:14:26.639
Your Majesty, you enjoy robust health.

00:14:27.399 --> 00:14:29.000
There are no signs of poisoning.

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:33.559
The sovereign's word is law.

00:14:34.919 --> 00:14:36.759
I've been severely unwell
these past days.

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:40.399
Are you suggesting
there's nothing wrong with me?

00:14:41.559 --> 00:14:42.000
Yes.

00:14:42.159 --> 00:14:42.879
Yes.

00:14:43.519 --> 00:14:45.240
It's merely my limited knowledge.

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:50.840
How is His Majesty?

00:14:51.960 --> 00:14:52.720
Your Majesty...

00:14:53.879 --> 00:14:56.600
The poison afflicting His Majesty
is exceptionally rare.

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:59.679
I need time to study it carefully.

00:15:13.679 --> 00:15:14.320
Your Highness,

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:16.080
Imperial Guard informants report.

00:15:16.799 --> 00:15:18.639
The ambassador sent
by Qi State's King Liang

00:15:19.080 --> 00:15:20.320
is not the Seventeenth Prince.

